    <item>
      <title>[高等数学] 13.定积分</title>
      <link>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/13.%E5%AE%9A%E7%A7%AF%E5%88%86/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/13.%E5%AE%9A%E7%A7%AF%E5%88%86/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[高等数学] 13.定积分</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="牛顿-莱布尼兹公式">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e7%89%9b%e9%a1%bf-%e8%8e%b1%e5%b8%83%e5%b0%bc%e5%85%b9%e5%85%ac%e5%bc%8f"></a>
牛顿-莱布尼兹公式
</h2>$$
\int_{a}^{b} f(x) \, dx = F(x)\bigg|_{a}^{b} = F(b) - F(a)
$$<blockquote>
<p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/13.%E5%AE%9A%E7%A7%AF%E5%88%86/image-20260703160842655.png" alt="image-20260703160842655"></p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="换元法">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%8d%a2%e5%85%83%e6%b3%95"></a>
换元法
</h2><p>换元时, <strong>同步更新</strong>上下限</p>
<h2 id="分部积分法">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%88%86%e9%83%a8%e7%a7%af%e5%88%86%e6%b3%95"></a>
分部积分法
</h2><p>核心公式:
</p>
$$
\int_{a}^{b} u v' \, dx = uv\bigg|_{a}^{b} - \int_{a}^{b} u' v \, dx
$$<ul>
<li>常用于u和v的函数形式不同时</li>
<li>选谁当u: 口诀<code>反, 对, 幂, 三, 指</code></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/13.%E5%AE%9A%E7%A7%AF%E5%88%86/image-20260703161930567.png" alt="image-20260703161930567"></p>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-07-03首发于<a href='https://byzhrichard.github.io/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-07-03</p>]]>
      </description>
      
        <category>高等数学</category>
      
    </item>
    
    

