        <![CDATA[<h1>[高等数学] 10.曲率及曲率半径</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="曲率及曲率半径">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%9b%b2%e7%8e%87%e5%8f%8a%e6%9b%b2%e7%8e%87%e5%8d%8a%e5%be%84"></a>
曲率及曲率半径
</h2><p>曲率$K$:
</p>
$$
K = \frac{|y''|}{\left[1+(y')^2\right]^{\frac{3}{2}}}
$$<p>
曲率半径$\rho$:
</p>
$$
\rho = \frac{1}{K}
$$<blockquote>
<p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/10.%E6%9B%B2%E7%8E%87%E5%8F%8A%E6%9B%B2%E7%8E%87%E5%8D%8A%E5%BE%84/image-20260703125959060.png" alt="image-20260703125959060"></p>
</blockquote>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-07-03首发于<a href='https://byzhrichard.github.io/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-07-03</p>]]>
